%N A193175 Numbers k such that there exists a two-dimensional generalized Bravais lattice with k-fold symmetry.
%C A193175 The complete list of 29 terms is shown. These are the values of 2n such that A193179(n)=1.
%C A193175 Along with 2, even numbers k such that the cyclotomic field Q(zeta_k) has class number 1. - _Jianing Song_, May 27 2026
